<h3>Simulated Conference on Computer Science and Engineering</h3>
<p>
                    The simulated conference on computer science and engineering is a virtual conference
                    for the students who take the course "COMPOSITION OF SCIENTIFIC THESIS". The conference will be
                    composed of best paper presentations and poster presentations, in
                    order to give the students a real experience of attending an international conference.
                </p>
