<p><h4>Poster Presentation</h4></p>
<p>
               ...
                </p>
<p>
<h4>	Paper Submission</h4><br/>
<br/>
<p>
                		1.Submit your final paper by group on <a href="https://www.easychair.org/">Easy Chair</a> before on <b><font color="#CD0000">Deciding...</font></b>.<br/>

                		3.Follow the steps <a href="submission.html">here</a> and upload your paper <b><font color="#1E90FF">as a new submission</font></b>.<br/>

						4.Every group should prepare a presentation or a poster for your paper.<br/>
					
						5.Students should show us your paper with presentation on the next two lessons.<br/>
</p>
</p>
<p>
                	Final Work:<br/>
<br/>
                	Every group with 1 to 3 students needs to submit a paper written by members of the group at the last phase of this course.
                	This paper can be one of your previous work or future work. In consideration of students' research progess,
                	the academic quality of the paper isn't much required. You may just describe your research and pay attention to
                	the format of the paper instead. The subjects can be found <a href="topics.html">here</a>.
                </p>
<p>
                	We use <a href="https://www.easychair.org/">Easy Chair</a> to take care of our conference. You can find the guide on its website or <a href="submission.html">here</a>.
                </p>
<p>
                	Announcements:<br/>
<br/>
                	(1) Write in English.<br/>
                	(2) Group members can't be more than three people.<br/>
                	(3)	Do not Copy.<br/>
</p>
